dc_title_s: Tōkyō shiku kaisei shukuzu zen; Tōkyō Fuchō.
dc_description_s: Mounted cover title. Lithograph In Japanese. Relief shown by hachures. Oriented with north to the upper right. Includes 2 insets and legend. 4 sheets joined. 1 map: col.; 64 x 81 cm, folded in cover 21 x 14 cm This map is in the public domain.
